\id 2TI - Matumbi Bible Version
\h 2 Timoteo
\toc1 Balua Yenebi'li' ya Pauli kwa Timoteo
\toc2 2 Timoteo
\toc3 2Tim
\mt1 2 Timoteo
\mt2 Balua Yenebi'li' ya Pauli kwa Timoteo
\c 1
\p 
\v 1 Balua yi'no niiandike nenga na Pauli, ntumilwe wa Kilisitu Yesu kwa mabinio ga Nnu'ngu'. Nitumilwe li'nga naabakiye bandu bu'kana na ukoto watulagilwe kwa kumwu'bi'lya Kilisitu Yesu.
\v 2 Nikuandikya wamwana wangu' waupendilwe Timoteo.
\p Nikulu'bya ngu'ngu', kiya na amani bu'ka kwa Tati' Nnu'ngu' na kwa Kilisitu Yesu Bwana witu ibe nawe.
\s1 Sukulu na mayi'gi'yo go senga
\p 
\v 3 Ninsukulu Nnu'ngu' nywanintumikia kwo binia ganannoga kati mwabaantumikiye au'ku' bangu'. Kilo na muntwekati nendakuku'mbu'kya mumalu'bo gangu'.
\v 4 Nigaku'mbu'kya moli gako, na nibile na kilu'lu' so bonagana kai' li'nga niupulaise muno mwoyo wangu'.
\v 5 Niiku'mbu'kya imani yako ya kakape yayaabile wi'ti' kwa mbuya bako Loisi na mau' bako Eunike. Niu'bi'lya panga kakape na wenga ubile nayo kai'.
\v 6 Kwa kitumbu si' nganikuku'mbu'ki'a uutili upo ya kiloo yawipokile panikubi'ki moko panani yako.
\v 7 Mwanjaa Nnu'ngu' atupeili loo ya bwoga, ila ya makakala, ya upendo no li'ngi'lya.
\p 
\v 8 Kwa nyo, kanewibone oni kong'ondelya makowe ga Bwana witu au kwa mwanjaa nibile muutabilwe bu'kana na ywembe. Ila, ulu'mbane na nenga mutabu ya Injili kwa makakala gaupeyelwa na Nnu'ngu'.
\v 9 Ywembe aatitukosopolya, na kutusawa tupange twabandu bake apeleteu. Aapangite nyo kwa kitumbu sa yendo yitu inannoga lili, ila kwo binia na kwa ngu'ngu' yake. Aatupei ngu'ngu' yo kwa ndi'la ya Kilisitu Yesu, kubile balo umbilwa kwa dunia.
\v 10 Na nambi'yambi' ngu'ngu' yo itanganikwe, kwo umukulilwa kwake nkosopoli witu Kilisitu Yesu ywaalabiye kiwo na kutulaya ukoto wangayomoka kwa ndi'la ya Abali Inannoga.
\p 
\v 11 Kwa kitumbu sa Abali Inannoga yo nisaulilwe nibe namwaali, ntumilwe, na mwalimu.
\v 12 Kwa kitumbu so nendaku'su'mbu'lwa, lakini niibonali oni kwa mwanjaa nintangite ywanimwu'bi'lile. Kai' nitangite panga endawesa kukili'ndi'la si'lu' saanikamukiye mpaka lisu'ba li'lu' lyo buyangana kwake.
\v 13 Ugakamwe mayi'gano ga kakape gaugayu'wine gapange kili'be so yigilwa pamope na imani, na upendo mu Kilisitu Yesu.
\v 14 Kwa makakala ga Loo Mpeleteu ywatama nkati yitu, ugali'ndi'le mayi'gano gano manogau gaukamukiyilwe.
\p 
\v 15 Utangite panga bandu boti ba kunkoa wa Asia banilei, nkati yabe babile Figelo na Helimogene.
\v 16 Bwana aabi'ki kiya alongo ba Onesiforo, kwa mwanjaa akokotyage isa kuniponwa moli na wala aibwenili oni kunibona nibile muutabilwe.
\v 17 Paaikite Roma bai, aakasine kunipala mpaka paanibweni.
\v 18 Na wenga ugatangite gambone gaanipangile akwo Efeso. Bwana ammi'ki kiya mulisu'ba lyake lyo buya.
\c 2
\s1 Asikali mwu'bi'li'ka wa Kilisitu Yesu
\p 
\v 1 Bai wamwana wangu', ube na makakala kwa ndi'la ya ngu'ngu' yatupata kwa Kilisitu Yesu.
\v 2 Ugatole mayi'gano gaugayu'wine kasangu' nnu'ngi' ya bandu bambone, na wenga wayi'gane bandu bawau'bi'lya, li'nga baakombwe kwayi'gana bi'ngi' kai'.
\v 3 Ulu'mbane na nenga mungu'su'mbu' kati asikali mwu'bi'li'ka wa Kilisitu Yesu.
\v 4 Asikali mana abile kungondo, apalikwa abe kuutalu na makowe ga maisa ga kila lisu'ba, li'nga kumpulaisa mpi'ndo wake.
\v 5 Mundu ywoywoti ywasindana ming'ando yo butuka lubi'lo, akombwali pata upo yo sinda mana akotwike koleya salya ya ming'ando yake.
\v 6 Nni'mi ywakasana muuli'mi ngaywapalikwa pata mili'mbu' ya mauno gake.
\v 7 Ugataunikiye ago ganigalongela, na Bwana aakupeya uweso wa kugatanga makowe galu' goti.
\p 
\v 8 Unku'mbu'ki Yesu Kilisitu wa lubelekwo lwa Daudi ywayu'yilwe bu'ka kuuwi'li, kati mwaibaya Abali Inannoga yaniala.
\v 9 Bu'kana na go nendaku'su'mbu'lwa ata baa muutabilwe kati nannau, lakini liyi'gi'yo lya Nnu'ngu' litabilwali.
\v 10 Kwa nyo nendakomeya goti kwa kitumbu sa babasaulilwe na Nnu'ngu' li'nga nabembe babe na ukosopoli waubile kwa Kilisitu Yesu, pamope na utukupu wangayomoka.
\v 11 Mayi'gi'yo ga, ga kakape panga,
\q1 Mana twaawile pamope nakwe
\q2 twaalama nakwe kai'.
\q1 
\v 12 Mana twaakomeya
\q2 twaatawala nakwe.
\q1 Mana twaankana
\q2 naywembe aatukana.
\q1 
\v 13 Mana twau'bi'li'ka lili,
\q2 ywembe balo aau'bi'li'ka,
\q2 kwa mwanjaa akombwali kwikana.
\s1 Mpangakasi ywayi'ki'tilwe na Nnu'ngu'
\p 
\v 14 Waku'mbu'ki'ye aumini makowe go na kwakwi'li'ka nnu'ngi' ya Nnu'ngu' panga bakotoke taukana bu'kana na mayi'gi'yo. Mitau ntu'pu' pwaila, ila yaalabiya babapi'kania.
\v 15 Ukasane li'nga wilaye panga uyi'ki'tilwe na Nnu'ngu' kati mpangakasi ywangali kwibona oni, ywayi'gana kwa ukakape liyi'gi'yo lya Nnu'ngu'.
\v 16 Wibi'ke kuutalu na mayi'gi'yo gabule ga mudunia, kwa mwanjaa ago gaapanga bandu babe kuutalu na Nnu'ngu'.
\v 17 Mayi'gano gabe gendatema kati libanga lya matana. Nkati ya babayi'gana go, babile ki Himenayo na Fileto,
\v 18 babailei kakape kababaya panga uyu'ki witu upite, no alabiya imani ya bandu bi'ngi'.
\v 19 Lakini nsingi wa Nnu'ngu' wauyi'mi wisowiso uandikilwe kwa mayi'gi'yo aga, “Bwana aatangite bababile bake,” na, “Kila ywaibaya ywembe ywa Bwana, auleke ulau.”
\p 
\v 20 Muliku'ta kubile na yombo ya samani bai lili, ila na yangali samani, yi'ngi' itumika kwa makowe ga ngama, na yi'ngi' kwa kila lisu'ba.
\v 21 Mundu mana aipeletiye kwa kugaleka malau goti, aapanga sombo sa ngama no saulilwa, kai' sendapwaika kwa lyengo lya Bwana no yi'ma wisowiso kwo panga makowe goti manogau.
\v 22 Ugaleke maminyikio malau ga unsembe wako, ukoteye makowe ga aki, imani, upendo na amani pamope na bandu babankilikitya Bwana kwa myoyo mipeleteu.
\v 23 Wibi'ke kuutalu na mitau ya kilogeloge yangali maana, kwa mwanjaa mitau iwesa leta bulwe.
\v 24 Kai' ntumisi wa Bwana apalikwali abe munomo, ila abe nnogau kwa bandu boti, ywakombwa yi'gana na kwakomeya bandu.
\v 25 Apalikwa kwakwi'li'ka bandu babantaukya, ila kwa ukali'li. Pi'ngi' Nnu'ngu' aawesa kwayalya galambuka na kwitanga kweli.
\v 26 Bu'kapo bawesa pata malango no ku'su'pu'ka mukitapa sa Ibilisi saayonjike kwo panga bapange mwapendi ywembe.
\c 3
\s1 Masu'ba ga kuundi'la
\p 
\v 1 Nambi'yambi' utange panga, masu'ba ga kuundi'la kwalu'a baa na nsimu wa tabu.
\v 2 Kwa mwanjaa bandu baalu'a kwipenda bene, baapenda mbanje, baalu'a kwilumba, babaa bene umbu'ku'su', balu'a baa atukani, bangali kwayu'wa abelei babe, bangali sukulu, bangali kumwisimu Nnu'ngu',
\v 3 bangali kwapenda ayabe, bangali penda awana, abai, bangali li'ngi'lya, akali', babakana manogau,
\v 4 asongi, kingayu'wa, babaipuna, babapenda muno maminyikio ga dunia kulikoni kumpenda Nnu'ngu'.
\v 5 Babonekana kati bandu bababi'ngi'ya gapala Nnu'ngu', lakini bagakana makakala gake. Kwa nyo utame kuutalu na bandu kati bo.
\v 6 Nkati yabe babile babayingya mumayumba ga bandu na kwakonga alwawa alalo babatopilwe na masambi kabautilwa na maminyikio ga kila sampuli.
\v 7 Alwawa bo bapala kwiyi'gana kila lisu'ba, lakini bakombwali kuutanga ukakape.
\v 8 Bandu ba bautaukya ukakape kati mwabantauki Musa ki Yane na Yambre. Bandu bo malango gabe gatitindigana na imani yabe ipwaikali.
\v 9 Lakini baayendelyali muno, kwa mwanjaa ulogeloge wabe waabonekana kwa bandu mpu'la, kati mwaubonekine ulogeloge wa balu' analu'me abi'li'.
\s1 Malagyo ga kuundi'la
\p 
\v 10 Ila wenga ukoleyite mayi'gano gangu', nnyendo wangu', binia kwangu', imani yangu', ukomeyi wangu', upendo wangu', na uli'ndi wangu'.
\v 11 Utangite bandu mwabaniawiye na siki yaniipatike panaabile muilambo ya Antiokia, Ikonio na Lustila. Naatikomea goti, na Bwana Yesu nganikosopolya mu ago goti.
\v 12 Kakape, boti babamwu'bi'lya Kilisitu Yesu no pala panga maisa gapala Nnu'ngu' baalu'a ku'su'mbu'lwa.
\v 13 Lakini bandu alau na akongi baayendelya muno panga ulau, baalu'a kwakonga no kongelwa.
\v 14 Lakini wenga uyendeli tama mu'lu' muukakape wauyi'ganilwe na kuuyi'ki'tya, kwa mwanjaa utangite wiyi'ganiye go bu'ka kwa nyai.
\v 15 Bu'ka kuunangu'ta, ugatangite Maandiko Mapeleteu. Ago gakupanga utange panga ukosopoli upatikana kwa kumwu'bi'lya Kilisitu Yesu.
\v 16 Maandiko Mapeleteu goti gaandikilwe kwa ulongosi wa Nnu'ngu' na gapwaika kwo yi'gana ukakape, kwi'li'ka no goloya mayi'gano, no longoya bandu batame mumaisa ga aki.
\v 17 Maandiko gano gaapanga bandu ba Nnu'ngu' baibi'ke wiso no timya kwo panga manogau goti.
\c 4
\p 
\v 1 Nikulagya nnu'ngi' ya Nnu'ngu' na Kilisitu Yesu ywaalu'a kwaukumu akoti na awi'li, na ngaywaalu'a isa tawala abile nkulungwa.
\v 2 Uale liyi'gi'yo lya Nnu'ngu'. Utame wiso munsimu waupwaika na wangali pwaika. Ukalipi, ukwi'li'ke na wakangamaye bandu. Upange nyo ku'no kauyi'gana kwa ukomeyi woti.
\v 3 Nikubakia panga ulu'a isa nsimu wa bandu kugakana mayi'gano ga kakape, kabapala gabapendi bene no sawa balimu baingi bo yi'gana gabagapendi kugapi'kania mumakutu gabe.
\v 4 Baakana pi'kania ukakape no koleya u'mo ya ubu'su'.
\v 5 Lakini wenga utame kwo li'ngi'lya mumakowe goti. Ukomeye ngu'su'mbu', uale Abali Inannoga, na upange kinannoga muutumisi wako woti.
\p 
\v 6 Kwa mwanjaa nibi'ki'lwa wiso kati salaka, no yomoka kwangu' kuegelile.
\v 7 Nitekasana mumasindano, mwanja niuyomolile na imani yangu' niikotike.
\v 8 Na nambi'yambi' nipi'kanilya peyelwa taji ya aki. Bwana, nga akimu wa aki, aanipeya lisu'ba lyo buya kwake. Ayo napeyelwa nenga bai lili, ila na boti babamwu'bi'lya kwa kilu'lu' paabuya.
\s1 Malagyo
\p 
\v 9 Ukasane isa kasangu' kiyu'ngu'ya.
\v 10 Kwa mwanjaa Dema agapendi makowe ga padunia, nganileka no yenda ku Tesalonike. Kreske aayi'i Galatia, na Tito aayi'i Dalmatia.
\v 11 Luka kisake ngaywaaigali nanenga pano. Pawisa ku'no ulongwane na Maluko kwa mwanjaa endapwaika kwa kuniyangatia mulyengo lya Nnu'ngu'.
\v 12 Naantumike Tikiko yenda ku Efeso.
\v 13 Pawalu'a isa wanipu'tu'li likoti lyanalilei Tiloa kwa Kalpo, na itabu, munomuno itabu yi'lu' ya maki'ngo.
\p 
\v 14 Alekisanda pundi kipala aanipangi maakau gambone. Bwana alu'a kunni'pa bu'kana na mwapangite.
\v 15 Wili'ndi'le bu'kana na ywembe, kwa mwanjaa aatigataukya muno mayi'gano gitu.
\p 
\v 16 Panitumbwi kwikengya ntu'pu' mundu ywaaniyi'mile, boti baatinileka. Ninnu'ba Nnu'ngu' kaneabalangili likosa lyo!
\v 17 Lakini Bwana Yesu aabile na nenga. Aanipei makakala go ala Abali Inannoga li'nga bandu bangali Ayahudi wapate kwiyu'wa. Aanikosopoli mukiwo, kwa mwanjaa naai kati nibile pankano wa imba.
\v 18 Bwana aalu'a yendelya kunikosopolya mumaakau goti na kunili'ndi'la mpaka panaaika muukulungwa wake wa kunani. Bwana Yesu akwi'yi'lwe milele na milele. Amina.
\s1 Salamu ya kuundi'la
\p 
\v 19 Wapei salamu ki Priska, Akula na alongo ba Onesiforo.
\v 20 Elasito aaigali Kolinto, Tilofimo naanei Mileto kwa mwanjaa aai ntamwe.
\p 
\v 21 Uyu'mbi'ti'ke isa kipepwe kibile balo. Eubulo, Pude, Linusi, Klaudia na aumini boti bakupei salamu.
\p 
\v 22 Bwana Yesu abe na wenga. Ngu'ngu' ya Nnu'ngu' ibe namwe.
